metadata.name: Kanyudunks Unrevealed #1
metadata.description: Kanyudunks is a collection of 5555 nfts that aims to provide exceptional web 2 & 3 masterclass gaming experiences rather than merely being cute pfps. The voyage of KanyuDunks aims to create a wide spectrum of iconic NBA players and introduce them all to the Metaverse. Kanyudunks NFTs will participate in the game as playable characters and get native token awards, NFT rarities and partners WL. By April 15, our holders who might be interested in attending the playoffs will also have access to NBA playoff tickets (at capped supply). Those ticket winners who are unable to attend may choose to resell their tickets using our chosen ticket inventory options. For more information, please visit our website http://kanyudunksnfts.com/
